Untitled (defaced Join) was a Rebel Alliance
propaganda poster created by Mandalorian artist Sabine Wren. The design was based on Join, a recruitment poster created by Coba Dunivee for the Galactic Empire. Although similar to the regular Join poster, there were some key differences: In particular, the "Join" word was obscured by a painted on stylized version of "Rebels", with a blue starbird at the bottom right corner, and the stormtrooper helmet was obscured by a "no" sign.
